item.title: Q-Sets, \Delta-Sets, and L-Spaces
item.description: arXiv:2501.08298v2 Announce Type: replace Abstract: The question whether there is a Lindelof Q-set space or Lindelof $\Delta$-set space is considered. We show that J. Moore's ZFC $L$-space is not a Q-set space in ZFC and, assuming all Aronszajn trees are special, it is not a $\Delta$-set space.
item.dc:creator: Pourya Memarpanahi, Paul Szeptycki
